<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Farmer Government Schemes</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="scheme.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>Government Schemes for Farmers</h1>
            <p>Empowering Farmers with Knowledge</p>
        </header>
        <section id="schemes" class="schemes">
            <div class="scheme-card">
                <h3>Pradhan Mantri Fasal Bima Yojana</h3>
                <p>Crop Insurance Scheme for farmers, offering financial support in case of crop loss.</p>
                <button>Learn More</button>
            </div>
            <div class="scheme-card">
                <h3>Kisan Credit Card (KCC)</h3>
                <p>Provides timely credit to farmers to meet their agricultural and ancillary needs.</p>
                <button>Learn More</button>
            </div>
            <div class="scheme-card">
                <h3>Pradhan Mantri Krishi Sinchai Yojana</h3>
                <p>Aims at providing irrigation facilities to every village in the country.</p>
                <button>Learn More</button>
            </div>
            <div class="scheme-card">
                <h3>Paramparagat Krishi Vikas Yojana</h3>
                <p>Promotes organic farming in clusters to improve soil health and yield quality.</p>
                <button>Learn More</button>
            </div>
            <div class="scheme-card">
                <h3>Soil Health Card Scheme</h3>
                <p>Provides soil health cards to farmers to monitor the nutrient status of their soil.</p>
                <button>Learn More</button>
            </div>
            <div class="scheme-card">
                <h3>Pradhan Mantri Kisan Samman Nidhi</h3>
                <p>Provides income support to farmers' families with a direct cash transfer scheme.</p>
                <button>Learn More</button>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
